span>\n<span id=\"cb4-4\"><a href=\"#cb4-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"programando-em-python\">Programando em: Python</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>N\u00e3o tem a necessidade de informar o tipo</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb5\"><pre class=\"sourceCode py\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb5-1\"><a href=\"#cb5-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>operador <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"bu\">input</span>()</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"programando-em-typescript\">Programando em: TypeScript</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>N\u00e3o tem a necessidade de informar o tipo</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb6\"><pre class=\"sourceCode ts\"><code class=\"sourceCode typescript\"><span id=\"cb6-1\"><a href=\"#cb6-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">let</span> operador <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"fu\">input</span>()<span class=\"op\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"resolu\u00e7\u00e3o\">Resolu\u00e7\u00e3o</h2>\n<h3 id=\"em-c\">Em C++</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W5JJ_NccMkM\">V\u00eddeo</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body>\n</html>",
